          "style": "Normal"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " ",
        "formatting": {},
        "metadata": {
          "style": "Normal"
        }
      }
    ],
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "In order to be successful with a focused differentiation strategy, the product enhancements added to the products must provide true value to customers, and all of the functions supporting this strategy, such as supply chain and research and development, must align. If Natco Pharmaceuticals executes properly on this strategy, they should continue to grow and effectively compete in a challenging industry.",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "In order to be successful with a focused differentiation strategy, the product enhancements added to the products must provide true value to customers, and all of the functions supporting this strategy, such as supply chain and research and development, must align. If Natco Pharmaceuticals executes properly on this strategy, they should continue to grow and effectively compete in a challenging industry.",
        "formatting": {},
        "metadata": {
          "style": "Normal"
        }
      }
    ],
    "metadata": {}
  },
