  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Introduction",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Introduction",
        "formatting": {
          "bold": true
        },
        "metadata": {
          "style": "Normal"
        }
      }
    ],
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "GreenTech Industries is facing a unique challenge due to the convergence of various pressures, including environmental regulations and increased demand for eco-friendly products. The second main pressure on GreenTech is that of rising commodity prices, which are rising at the same time.  Now, instead of reacting to multiple pressures at once, GreenTech should prioritize its response to the above issues through the concept of strategic interdependence, where the company can focus on those areas of the business that have a positive effect on the other pressures as well as on the entire organization.",
    "children": [
