  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "3. Recommendation: Focus on Related Diversification with Cautious Expansion",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "3. Recommendation: Focus on Related Diversification with Cautious Expansion",
        "formatting": {
          "bold": true
        },
        "metadata": {
          "style": "Normal"
        }
      }
    ],
    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Unrelated diversification is when you move into entirely new industries, which can include a current business. An example of this would be if you decided to enter the fintech or digital health sectors. Some of the advantages of this type of strategy include providing the opportunity to spread risk between different industries, as well as allowing for access into some very fast-growing industries with the potential of very high returns down the road.",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Unrelated diversification is when you move into entirely new industries, which can include a current business. An example of this would be if you decided to enter the fintech or digital health sectors. Some of the advantages of this type of strategy include providing the opportunity to spread risk between different industries, as well as allowing for access into some very fast-growing industries with the potential of very high returns down the road.",
        "formatting": {},
        "metadata": {
          "style": "Normal"
        }
      }
