    "metadata": {}
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Some of the disadvantages of this type of strategy include potentially not having enough knowledge and/or experience to manage these new types of industries; attempting to manage these disparate types of businesses increases complexity; and without sufficient knowledge, additional links exist that could result in failure.",
    "children": [
      {
