    "text": "1. Better Quality and Strong Brand ImageThe company relies heavily upon a single supplier for high-quality products to ensure the food product has consistent quality. In the case of launching a new kitchen appliance, first impressions are critical; if a new cookware line has a reputation for having high-quality and consistent products, customers will be more likely to identify with and trust the brand.",
