    "text": "Conversely, the company’s use of multiple suppliers increases the risk of the varying quality of products impacting customer satisfaction; thus, there is an increased likelihood of defective items being sent out (which can increase return rates and generate additional expenditures on manufacturers’ warranties).",
    "children": [
      {
